  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/42fd2a3d476a10ce109f6fca09eaa797.avif?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=69 /></span></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/bd9a753d443e64aed4f57f858def94a7.poster.avif?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/bd9a753d443e64aed4f57f858def94a7.webm?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/bd9a753d443e64aed4f57f858def94a7.mp4?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Become the master of car parkour! <strong>Tails Noir: Rebel Rush</strong> is a <strong>speedrunning precision platformer</strong> where you speed through a flooded vision of Vancouver, jumping on buildings, inventing crazy shortcuts, in an effort to become the fastest driver in the city!<br> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/27b6b440ea499aface6a34944c218d35.poster.avif?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/27b6b440ea499aface6a34944c218d35.webm?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/27b6b440ea499aface6a34944c218d35.mp4?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/2000cfcb203ca930f4c7129a00217e81.webp?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=57 /></span><br>Push the pedal to the metal, hit those green boost panels and dash through the air with the whooshing sound! Complete the main path and immediately learn that the game has just begun!<br> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/e191846f18005b8a35a313f84325f78e.poster.avif?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/e191846f18005b8a35a313f84325f78e.webm?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/e191846f18005b8a35a313f84325f78e.mp4?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/64e298093275a64ee6691b1ddb3c7658.webp?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=61 /></span><br>Study the layouts of the twisted levels and figure out how to complete them faster! Find the hearts that will guide you to secrets and hidden paths, and <strong>invent your own crazy shortcuts</strong> to beat the global leaderboard (and your friends!!!)<br> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/380ebe982965866efa9318f3fdd3ea77.poster.avif?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/380ebe982965866efa9318f3fdd3ea77.webm?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/380ebe982965866efa9318f3fdd3ea77.mp4?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/3c7497e0b17319a93376a817a0366a9a.webp?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br>Master the chaos that surrounds you! Fall off the road because of one stupid mistake, <strong>scream elegantly</strong>, and get back on track like nothing happened!<br> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/f1d2474beac0237e112d24d984c40325.poster.avif?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/f1d2474beac0237e112d24d984c40325.webm?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/f1d2474beac0237e112d24d984c40325.mp4?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/8c46c21c3b7b5f0707869d9fc9d7b851.webp?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=63 /></span><br><strong>Remember</strong>: walls are for those who can be stopped by them. So go ahead, break some stuff, pave new roads, and have fun causing chaos in a world full of cops!<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/f12c3843d6a4b372ce934cae302ce41a.avif?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=75 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/abbbdaaaaebd92f990c1f5ffa693d72d.webp?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=61 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>4-6 hours</strong> of gameplay<br></li><li> <strong>19</strong> twisted <strong>levels</strong> of secret shortcuts, police barricades and surreal mayhem.<br></li><li> <strong>Highly replayable levels</strong> where you beat your times by going off roads and inventing clever shortcuts.<br></li><li> <strong>That’s not a racing game</strong>: our cars can double jump, they dash and bounce off buildings.<br></li><li> <strong>Friends & global leaderboards</strong>, and an official entry on the main speedrunning website in the world.<br></li><li> Yes, we really took the gloomy pixel art world of <strong>Tails Noir</strong> and turned it around into a bright, fun, car driving game.<br></li><li> Breakcore & drum and bass soundtrack full of bangers.<br></li><li> A good steering wheel that doesn't fly off while you're driving.</li></ul>",
